// ChatPanel
// Always-visible split panel combining the chat message area, input controls, and an embedded terminal.
// Used as the main chat UI in non-drawer contexts (e.g., desktop split-pane layout).

FUNCTION createActionHandler() -> ActionCallback
  Returns a callback that dispatches action responses to chatStore.

---

FUNCTION handleSendMessage(text)
  Sends a new user message via chatStore.

---

FUNCTION handleClearMessages()
  Clears the chat message history via chatStore.

---

FUNCTION renderContent() -> ReactNode
  Renders the message list and input controls inside a SplitPane with the terminal.

---

FUNCTION ChatPanel(props) -> ReactNode                                    EXPORT
  CALLS: useChatStore (chatStore), useUIStore (uiStore), useSessionStore (sessionStore), AIUIRenderer (renderer), MessageArea (MessageArea), SplitPane (SplitPane), TerminalTabsContainer (TerminalTabsContainer)
  Reads chat state from chatStore, UI layout state from uiStore, session from sessionStore.
  Renders a SplitPane with the chat area above and the terminal below (or side-by-side, based on layout).
  Passes the action handler to AI UI components.
